# 🧭 Basic Directions

```text
            North
              ↑

West    ←     ●     → East

              ↓
            South
```

---

# 💡 Concepts

### Right Turn

```text
North → East

East → South

South → West

West → North
```

### Left Turn

```text
North → West

West → South

South → East

East → North
```

---

# 🧠 Memory Trick

```text
RIGHT TURN

N → E

E → S

S → W

W → N

-----------------

LEFT TURN

N → W

W → S

S → E

E → N
```

---

# 📌 Important Rules

### Four Right Turns

```text
Same Direction
```

### Four Left Turns

```text
Same Direction
```

### Two Right Turns

```text
Opposite Direction
```

### Two Left Turns

```text
Opposite Direction
```

