# 📝 Introduction

Direction Sense questions test your ability to determine the **final direction** or **position** after moving in different directions.

These questions are frequently asked in placement exams such as:

- TCS
- Infosys
- Accenture
- Cognizant
- Capgemini
- Wipro
- Deloitte

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# 🧭 Basic Directions

```text
                 North
                   ↑
                   |
West  ←────────────┼────────────→  East
                   |
                   ↓
                 South
```

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# 📘 Right Turn Rule

Whenever you turn right, move clockwise.

```text
North
   ↓
East
   ↓
South
   ↓
West
   ↓
North
```

Memory Trick

```text
N → E → S → W
```

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# 📘 Left Turn Rule

Whenever you turn left, move anti-clockwise.

```text
North
   ↓
West
   ↓
South
   ↓
East
   ↓
North
```

Memory Trick

```text
N → W → S → E
```

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# 🌍 Real-Life Example

Suppose you start from your home.

```text
