# ❌ Common Mistakes

### Mistake 1

Confusing Left with Right.

Remember

```text
Right

↓

Clockwise

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Left

↓

Anti-clockwise
```

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

### Mistake 2

Trying to solve all turns mentally.

Correct Method

```text
One Turn

↓

Update Direction

↓

Next Turn
```

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

### Mistake 3

Ignoring the starting direction.

Always begin from the given direction before applying turns.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# 🎯 Interview Tips

Always solve Direction Sense questions using this order:

```text
Starting Direction

↓

Walk

↓

Turn

↓

Update Direction

↓

Repeat

↓

Final Direction
```

Never skip any step.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

